类 BaseItemAnimator

    • RecyclerView.ItemAnimator

    ScaleInOutItemAnimator, SlideInOutBottomItemAnimator, SlideInOutLeftItemAnimator, SlideInOutRightItemAnimator, SlideInOutTopItemAnimator, SlideScaleInOutRightItemAnimator

    public abstract class BaseItemAnimator
extends RecyclerView.ItemAnimator
    This implementation of android.support.v7.widget.RecyclerView.ItemAnimator provides basic animations on remove, add, and move events that happen to the items in a RecyclerView.
    另请参阅:
    android.support.v7.widget.RecyclerView#setItemAnimator(android.support.v7.widget.RecyclerView.ItemAnimator)
